18#include "Result.h"
19#include "DecoderResult.h"
20#include "TextDecoder.h"
21
22#include <utility>
23
24namespace ZXing {
25
26Result::Result(std::wstring&& text, Position&& position, BarcodeFormat format, ByteArray&& rawBytes)
27 : _format(format), _text(std::move(text)), _position(std::move(position)), _rawBytes(std::move(rawBytes))
28{
29 _numBits = Size(_rawBytes) * 8;
30}
31
32Result::Result(const std::string& text, int y, int xStart, int xStop, BarcodeFormat format, ByteArray&& rawBytes)
33 : Result(TextDecoder::FromLatin1(text), Line(y, xStart, xStop), format, std::move(rawBytes))
34{}
35
36Result::Result(DecoderResult&& decodeResult, Position&& position, BarcodeFormat format)
37 : _status(decodeResult.errorCode()), _format(format), _text(std::move(decodeResult).text()),
38 _position(std::move(position)), _rawBytes(std::move(decodeResult).rawBytes()), _numBits(decodeResult.numBits())
39{
40 if (!isValid())
41 return;
42
43 //TODO: change ResultMetadata::put interface, so we can move from decodeResult?
44 const auto& byteSegments = decodeResult.byteSegments();
45 if (!byteSegments.empty()) {
46 metadata().put(ResultMetadata::BYTE_SEGMENTS, byteSegments);
47 }
48 const auto& ecLevel = decodeResult.ecLevel();
49 if (!ecLevel.empty()) {
50 metadata().put(ResultMetadata::ERROR_CORRECTION_LEVEL, ecLevel);
51 }
52 if (decodeResult.hasStructuredAppend()) {
53 metadata().put(ResultMetadata::STRUCTURED_APPEND_SEQUENCE, decodeResult.structuredAppendSequenceNumber());
54 metadata().put(ResultMetadata::STRUCTURED_APPEND_CODE_COUNT, decodeResult.structuredAppendCodeCount());
55 metadata().put(ResultMetadata::STRUCTURED_APPEND_PARITY, decodeResult.structuredAppendParity());
56 }
57 //TODO: what about the other optional data in DecoderResult?
58}
59
60} // ZXing
